1. *Umro* je pre mesec dana. (He died a month ago.)
2. Njegov otac *umro* je pre dve godine. (His father died two years ago.)
3. Moja baba *umrla* je pre pet godina. (My grandmother died five years ago.)
4. *Umrla* je bez naslova. (She died without title.)
5. *Umre* li neko pre dvadeset godina? (Did anyone die twenty years ago?)
6. Nisam znao da je *umro*. (I didn't know he had died.)
7. *Umirali* su od gladi. (They were dying of hunger.)
8. *Umiru* li deca od bolesti? (Are children dying of diseases?)